        Conjunctional Sales in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know About Buyer's Agents
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Buyer's agents are becoming more common in Brisbane's inner east. Understanding how conjunctional sales work, who pays what, and what your Form 6 says about it matters before you sign.
      </p>
